This repository will teach you how to
- Contribute to someone else's repository: 
  - http://kbroman.org/github_tutorial/pages/fork.html
  - https://github.com/sevntu-checkstyle/sevntu.checkstyle/wiki/Development-workflow-with-Git:-Fork,-Branching,-Commits,-and-Pull-Request
- Use heroku with github: 
  - To use Heroku, read this: https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/getting-started-with-nodejs#deploy-the-app
  - To use Heroku & Github at same time: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/15231937/heroku-and-github-at-the-same-time
